OL,3,CRobbery in England and Wales rises
OL,4,Cback to pre-pandemic levels
OL,6,FCases of violence with injury also
OL,7,Freturned to pre-pandemic levels,
OL,8,Fincreasing to an estimated 562,000
OL,9,Fincidents in 2024 from around 376,000
OL,10,Fincidents the previous year.
OL,12,FOffences involving firearms have
OL,13,Fdecreased compared to last year, the
OL,14,Fdata shows, while those involving
OL,15,Fknives and sharp objects have gone up
OL,16,Fby 4%.
