OL,3,CRobbery in England and Wales rises
OL,4,Cback to pre-pandemic levels
OL,6,FWhile the rate of overall theft
OL,7,Fremained the same, data from the ONS
OL,8,Falso found incidents of "snatch theft"
OL,9,Fhad more doubled between 2023 and 2024
OL,10,Fcompared to the year prior. The number
OL,11,Fof incidents jumped from 32,000 to
OL,12,Fapproximately 78,000, a rise of 144%.
OL,14,FMore than 469,000 shoplifting offences
OL,15,Fwere recorded between June 2023 and
OL,16,FJune 2024, up from around 365,000
OL,17,Fincidents between June 2022 and June
OL,18,F2023.
