OL,3,CRobbery in England and Wales rises
OL,4,Cback to pre-pandemic levels
OL,6,F"Too many town centres have been
OL,7,Fdecimated by record levels of
OL,8,Fshoplifting, and communities have been
OL,9,Fleft shaken by rising levels of knife
OL,10,Fcrime, snatch theft and robbery. This
OL,11,Fcannot continue.
OL,13,F"This Government will restore
OL,14,Fneighbourhood policing across the
OL,15,Fcountry, put thousands more dedicated
OL,16,Fofficers out on our streets and scrap
OL,17,Fthe #200 shoplifting threshold,
OL,18,Fbringing an end to the effective
OL,19,Fimpunity for thieves who steal low
OL,20,Fvalue goods."
