OL,11,FITV News spoke to a shopkeeper who
OL,12,Fregularly falls victim to shoplifting.
OL,14,FPaul Cheema, who runs Malcolm's Stores
OL,15,FCostcutter in Coventry, had an
OL,16,Fincident where a person demanded money
OL,17,Ffrom the till: "Taking the money is
OL,18,Fone thing, but we're not here to be
OL,19,Fabused. We're here to provide a
OL,20,Fservice."
