OL,6,F"You get abused on a weekly basis.
OL,7,FNine out of ten times we let it go
OL,8,Fover our head because you then become
OL,9,Fdemoralised and we think 'what am I
OL,10,Fdoing this for anymore?' We're here
OL,11,Fbecause we love retail and we love our
OL,12,Fcommunity.
OL,14,F"I think the police response is pretty
OL,15,Fpoor. I'm not blaming the police...
OL,16,FThis is down to the resources that the
OL,17,Fpolice have got in Coventry, they
OL,18,Fcan't be everywhere at any one single
OL,19,Ftime. They do their best.
