OL,4,Cback to pre-pandemic levels
OL,6,F"The government must ensure that the
OL,7,Fstandalone offence for assaulting a
OL,8,Fretail worker passes into law as soon
OL,9,Fas possible to protect all retail
OL,10,Fworkers and to send a clear message
OL,11,Fthat this behaviour will not be
OL,12,Ftolerated. This will also give police
OL,13,Fthe data they need to allocate
OL,14,Fresources to tackle this epidemic we
OL,15,Fare currently facing."
OL,17,FFigures also show levels of crime
OL,18,Fexperienced by people have generally
OL,19,Fdecreased across the past ten years,
OL,20,Fwith some exceptions, including sexual
OL,21,Fassault.
